variables.name: DELETION_MODE_ALL
variables.comment: Deletion mode to delete all data associated with the selected records.

variables.name: DELETION_MODE_EXCLUDE_INTERNAL_DATA
variables.comment:
* Deletion mode to delete all data except the internal data (e.g. rate limits) for the selected
     * records.

variables.name: MATCH_BEHAVIOR_DELETE
variables.comment: Match behavior option to delete the supplied params (Origin/Domains).

variables.name: MATCH_BEHAVIOR_PRESERVE
variables.comment:
* Match behavior option to preserve the supplied params (Origin/Domains) and delete everything
     * else.

methods.name: public List<Uri> getDomainUris()
methods.comment: Get the list of domain URIs.

methods.name: public Instant getStart()
methods.comment: Get the start of the deletion range.

methods.name: public Instant getEnd()
methods.comment: Get the end of the deletion range.
